{"tid":1804331,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普及奧巴馬雙雙成為年度最受美國國民崇拜人物","createTime":"2019-12-31T02:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T03:58:58.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"43b1ea611c083c5eb3512cdc1afda5d8930a6975","tid":1804331,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:12:57.000Z","msg":"民調機構蓋洛普最新調查顯示，美國總統特朗普，及前任總統奧巴馬，雙雙成為2019年度，最受美國國民崇拜的人物。<br />\n<br />\n今次是特朗普首度成為國民最崇拜人物，奧巴馬就是第12次，兩人在這項年度調查中，都獲得18%國民認定是目前全球各地在生人士中，最受敬重的男性。<br />\n<br />\n支持特朗普的受訪者中，45%都是共和黨員，支持奧巴馬的人中，就有41%受訪者屬於民主黨。<br />\n<br />\n除了特朗普及奧巴馬外，其餘在前十名內的最受崇拜人物，支持率都不足2%，這些人物包括前總統卡特、微軟創辦人蓋茨、教宗方濟各、加州眾議員希夫、資深參議員桑德斯、股神巴菲特及達賴喇嘛等。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500240-20191231.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500240-20191231.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=84640f28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500240-20191231.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f8751e6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500240-20191231.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8ef7d58871169fbb39efedff37c3b7d8b01d9fc8","tid":1804331,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:13:23.000Z","msg":"標題黨<br />\nBTW<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7b599658531e94b6cef20b4ea8ae112e6c0e91","tid":1804331,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:16:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63e4e0e6d5445851217737ff0eabdf625007bbc","tid":1804331,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:21:46.000Z","msg":"支持特朗普的受訪者中，45%都是共和黨員，支持奧巴馬的人中，就有41%受訪者屬於民主黨。<br />\n<br />\n咁多人有黨背景？？唔係平民？"},{"pid":"95bcf2a76bf680f09523d40a